com.skratchdot.electribe.model.esx
Interface SongEvent

All Known Subinterfaces:
SongEventControl, SongEventDrumNote, SongEventKeyboardNote, SongEventMuteStatus, SongEventTempo
All Known Implementing Classes:
SongEventControlImpl, SongEventDrumNoteImpl, SongEventImpl, SongEventKeyboardNoteImpl, SongEventMuteStatusImpl, SongEventTempoImpl
public interface SongEvent

A representation of the model object 'Song Event'.

The following features are supported:

  • Current Position
  • Event Info
  • Event Type
  • Measure
  • Operation Number
  • Position Number
  • Step

See Also:
EsxPackage.getSongEvent()
